OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FA day of sunshine and
OL,6,Fscattered showers across the region.
OL,7,FThe showers possibly turning heavy in
OL,8,Fplaces with the risk of thunder.
OL,9,FRemaining on the rather cool side.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,12,FFurther sunshine and showers
OL,13,Fthroughout Wednesday before a spell of
OL,14,Fwet and windy weather moves in for
OL,15,FThursday. Potentially cloudy and damp
OL,16,Fto start Friday but drier and brighter
OL,17,Flater.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
